{"tid":780952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街梁美芬del比卡超comment兼block埋人","createTime":"2018-08-15T13:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T04:21:34.000Z","uid":138409,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5ed4bb211f2cde2878df496cf3c30b6b8ba8f7","tid":780952,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"事緣鼠王芬9up一輪畀人秒殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/779846/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/779846/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住就封殺人地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/1815797568533519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F1815797568533519&d=M8G5bui%2BjxuA9%2FsWM%2F8cFjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f3d1a0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/1815797568533519</a><br />\n<br />\n所以有勞各位將以下留言貼上去鼠王芬呢個post度 洗佢版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Leungmeifun/posts/1386638728134988?comment_id=1386957528103108&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R4%22%7D&amp;hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLeungmeifun%2Fposts%2F1386638728134988%3Fcomment_id%3D1386957528103108%26comment_tracking%3D%257B%2522tn%2522%253A%2522R4%2522%257D%26hc_location%3Dufi&d=M8G5bui%2BjxuA9%2FsWM%2F8cFjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f493eff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Leungmeifun/posts/1386638728134988?comment_id=1386957528103108&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R4%22%7D&amp;hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢block到幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">引述至Edward Wong 被刪之留言：<br />\n<br />\n／首先，Siracusa Principles的確「清楚詮釋了言論自由在國家安全問題前所收到的限制」。第29段清楚指出：「***只有在面臨武力或武力威脅情況下***保護民族生存、領土完整或政治獨立而採取限制某些人權的措施時，才能援引國家安全作為採取這些措施的理由。」<br />\n<br />\n第31段更特意強調：「不得利用國家安全作為藉口實行不明確或任意的限制，只有在具有防止濫用權利的充分保障和有效措施時，方得援引國家安全作為限制理由。」<br />\n<br />\n即使FCC真可被視作為陳浩天「提供政治宣傳的場所」，在無任何武力或武力威脅的情況下，「從法律角度」自然受言論自由保護，什麼「危害國家安全」，真不知從何說起。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Siracusa Principles並非International Commission of Jurists制定，ICJ（在美國的自治分部）只是召集／贊助人角色，召集各國人權專家討論了這些原則出來<br />\n<br />\n基本事實都可以錯，你地羞唔羞家㗎...／</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/215648_91ab6cb7222e72d917868bb186ebd087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F215648_91ab6cb7222e72d917868bb186ebd087.jpg&h=cb81ec64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72b4ad644f00b2fa306c3703ac550823d0bcdf23","tid":780952,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f5214f46380e4be854e0a210b3a0f8d7aaacec","tid":780952,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6caac8c6f3561569a321bb1a12c5267a0a266c","tid":780952,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060ac960645d1bb7282e07c26e1ff14a6bbdcc41","tid":780952,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6117a58ea1fa214f47ba3827b241e202410625af","t